      <title>LEMAIRE opened its Beijing Taikoo Li flagship on 10th March 2026. The boutique’s...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DV0XjflCHdU/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/650064143_18570343786019404_4806934524238389636_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1MTgwNjc0NDg3MTcyMjY4OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=ZrRk6mJzEiUQ7kNvwGtHN-A&amp;_nc_oc=Ado36eCP-gqjCNAUW6hPTXq6wBV5Pkvl7xMVcyAG5uNtBx21s3iJT_oq49p4qSfSNdI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6-P1-csrAioomZJ_9roAJg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzETiLEJ7sXopNkbtALol1qFofcgm_AuKZ_6g9UC4UV3g&amp;oe=69C98107" alt="Instagram billede fra @lemaire" /></p><p><strong>@lemaire</strong></p><p>LEMAIRE opened its Beijing Taikoo Li flagship on 10th March 2026. <br/>
<br/>
The boutique’s brutalist exterior frames the entrance to a space that balances domesticity with minimalist design. Inside, the furnishings juxtapose Chinese antiques with European modernism, continuing LEMAIRE’s dialogue between East and West, artists and artisans. <br/>
<br/>
LEMAIRE Beijing Taikoo Li flagship<br/>
Unit N4-10, Building 4, No. 11 Sanlitun Road, Chaoyang District, Beijing <br/>
<br/>
Photography @rino.qiu</p>]]></description>
